@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### NOTIFICATIONS MODULE - Alert & Notification System
### ============================================

### NOTIFICATIONS - List Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=1&limit=20&status=unread
Authorization: {{token}}

### NOTIFICATIONS - Get Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/summary
Authorization: {{token}}

### NOTIFICATIONS - Mark as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/:notificationId/read
Authorization: {{token}}

### NOTIFICATIONS - Mark All as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Notification types: alert, info, warning, success
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
